messages.message: I'm absolutely so proud of the impressive strides we are making with Instabase platform and bug fixes. Let's remember that we want our customers to know we are listening and delivering. How do we do that? Release notes! Team leads and devs, please add the Fix Version and release notes. See the Instabase docs wiki for our Release notes workflow (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/DOCS/pages/185696404/Release+notes), philosophy, and criteria. Questions? Please ask. The <#CM9TARK7U|> channel is always open.
